{"tid":120110,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（入黎幫下我）好掛住ex","createTime":"2017-02-14T08:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T16:21:59.000Z","uid":58294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b46f9b7a3d1f68e8d04fe76f978f49593017553e","tid":120110,"uid":58294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T08:15:53.000Z","msg":"今日係情人節 不過唔關事 係幾日前已經keep住呢個念頭<br />\n散左個幾月 大家冇搵大家<br />\n分手原因係佢覺得一齊太快 未了解清楚大家 個感覺好怪<br />\n我冇挽留 講到i don't fucking care 咁 <br />\n我都冇block佢d野 因為我一直都抱住要比佢知道我過得好好<br />\n如是者 我以為自己好潚灑 <br />\n直到前幾日 見到佢好快留意自己既野 突然好有感覺 後悔自己點解當日冇好好留佢(冇用啊嘛 我知 個陣)<br />\n我好想打去個佢好好咁傾<br />\n身邊冇人支持我咁做 但我知如果唔咁做我會後悔<br />\n當然做左都可能會<br />\n從來我都冇主動對佢做任何野 姐係就算係一齊個時都係 今次我想主動打比佢<br />\n今日唔係適當時候 我唔想佢唔會我係情人節系痕先搵佢 <br />\n聽日會唔會好d?"},{"pid":"fd4fa47ab9e99f33a8de05de9ef75378d4f5dd2e","tid":120110,"uid":58294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T08:17:34.000Z","msg":"我好辛苦"},{"pid":"5ae3bf6cc226844d74a1769657723a941dee8293","tid":120110,"uid":29589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T08:20:46.000Z","msg":"自作業"},{"pid":"33ddb3d05c4008c92192625d71ad7e9709530e73","tid":120110,"uid":58294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T08:25:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自作業</blockquote><br />\n屌醒我唔該"},{"pid":"403eaf3e0d3b8a2e5de91549132d6579ac18c7b3","tid":120110,"uid":58294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T08:35:37.000Z","msg":"有冇人理下我"},{"pid":"e6be3dfc2b3c2db34bc3f8060eddd25e1442fee0","tid":120110,"uid":58294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceed2404eb862f7527f92015423ecb19c24057a8","tid":120110,"uid":561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T08:38:58.000Z","m